rows.label: tlk43100143_04_msg0001
rows.name:
Everyone who managed to get out of
the way of the Superbian army is OK.
But my dad hasn't come back yet...

rows.label: tlk43100143_04_msg0002
rows.name:
We haven't heard from him. So we
don't know if he's OK, or if he's been
hurt...

rows.label: tlk43100143_04_msg0003
rows.name:
I'll never forget what the Superbians
did.

rows.label: tlk43100143_04_msg0004
rows.name:
When I'm a Driver, I'm gonna fight for
justice with a Light-type Blade! And I'll
teach those Superbians a thing or two!

rows.label: tlk43100143_04_msg0005
rows.name:
Huh? Light-type Blades are hard to
find, you say?

rows.label: tlk43100143_04_msg0006
rows.name:
But if I just set my mind to it, I'm
sure I'll be able to resonate with a
really awesome one.
